European Stocks Fall for Fourth Day; Travel, Construction Shares Decline

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-06-06T07:03:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/european-stocks-fall-for-fourth-day-travel-construction-shares-decline.html
European stocks retreated for a
fourth day, led by travel and construction companies, amid
growing concern the economy is weakening. The Stoxx Europe 600
Index dropped 0.4 percent to 272.52 at 8:02 a.m. in  London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
